    </div>
  </div>
</section>

   <section class="section team-section">
  <div class="container team-grid">

    <div class="team-image">
      <img
        src="/images/team/ceremony.png"
        alt="PRC Awards Ceremony"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="team-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow dark">Our Leadership</p>

      <h2>Recognized as Event Organizer of the Year</h2>

      <p>
        For the last 30 years, GIGI has been engaged in promotions,
        development communications, and mass media enterprises, with
        special emphasis in the production of hundreds of audio-visual
        support materials (AVP) and event management projects.
      </p>

      <p>
        As a seasoned event manager and Executive Producer, the Foundation
        for Outstanding Professionals, Inc. (FOP), in association with the
        Professional Regulation Commission (PRC), publicly acclaimed GIGI
        with the <strong>Event Organizer of the Year</strong> award under
        the PRC Awards 2020. The awarding ceremony was held on
        March 18, 2022 at The Manila Hotel.
      </p>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

    <section class="section light">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="eyebrow dark">Why Choose MMB?</p>

    <h2>Why Organizations Choose MMB</h2>

    <div class="why-grid">

      <div class="why-column">

        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Creative and Customized Event Concepts</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Professional Project Management</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Reliable Network of Trusted Suppliers</h3>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="why-column">

        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Attention to Every Detail</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Seamless Event Execution</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Personalized Client Service</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Commitment to Excellence</h3>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section featured">
  <div class="container">

    <p class="eyebrow dark">Featured Event</p>

    <div class="featured-photo">
      <img
        src="/images/featured/event1.jpg"
        alt="Corporate event by MMB Events"
      />
    </div>

  </div>
</section>


    <section id="contact" class="section contact">
      <div class="container narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Contact Us</p>
        <h2>"DETAIL IS NOT JUST A PRIORITY—IT IS AN OBSESSION."</h2>
        <p>At MMB Events, every celebration is more than an event—it is an experience thoughtfully designed, professionally managed, and passionately delivered. We are dedicated to turning your vision into unforgettable moments that leave lasting impressions.</p>
        <br><p>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@mmb-events.com">contact@mmb-events.com</a></p>
        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+639171008460">+63 917 100 8460</a></p>
        <p>Address: Concepcion Uno, Marikina City</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
.hero {
  min-height: 85vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;

  background:
  linear-gradient(
    rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.35),
    rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.45)
  ),
  url("/images/hero/hero.jpg");

  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;

  color: var(--white);
  padding: 90px 0;
}

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .eyebrow.dark {
    color: var(--maroon);
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 950px;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.8rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  h2 {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  h3 {
    color: var(--maroon);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .narrow h3 {
  margin-top: 28px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

  .lead,
  .narrow p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .lead {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 34px;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .light {
    background: var(--light);
  }

  .narrow {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .stats {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 34px 0;
  }

  .stat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .stat-grid strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 3rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-grid span {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 22px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  article {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .service-list {
  margin: 12px 0 0;
  padding-left: 20px;
}

.service-list li {
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  line-height: 1.45;
}

.service-list li:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

article p {
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

  .navy {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .navy h2 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .projects {
    margin-top: 20px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .contact {
    background: var(--maroon);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .contact h2 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .contact a {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

.team-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 420px 1fr;
  gap: 56px;
  align-items: start;
}

.team-image img {
  width: 100%;
  display: block;
  border-radius: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
}

.team-copy p {
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.trusted-copy {
  max-width: 720px;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.logo-marquee {
  width: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 40px;
  position: relative;
}

.trusted-label {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  margin-top: 42px;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.logo-track {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 24px;
  width: max-content;
  animation: marquee 32s linear infinite;
}

.logo-track img {
  width: 170px;
  height: 80px;
  object-fit: contain;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  transition: transform .25s ease;
}

.logo-track img:hover {
  transform: scale(1.06);
}

.logo-marquee:hover .logo-track {
  animation-play-state: paused;
}

@keyframes marquee {
  from {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  to {
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
}

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .stat-grid,
    .service-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .team-grid {
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
}

    .hero {
      min-height: auto;
      padding: 90px 0;
    }
  }

  .about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 420px;
  gap: 56px;
  align-items: start;
}


.about-award img {
  width: 100%;
  display: block;
  border-radius: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
}

.about-copy p {
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.why-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 60px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}

.why-column {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.why-item {
  padding: 18px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(199, 154, 74, 0.45);
}

.why-item:first-child {
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(199, 154, 74, 0.45);
}

.why-item h3 {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--navy);
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.values-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: start;
}

.values-photo img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 520px;
  display: block;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
}

.values-list {
  margin-top: 36px;
}

.value-item {
  padding: 26px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(199,154,74,.35);
}

.value-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(199,154,74,.35);
}

.value-item h3 {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  color: var(--maroon);
  font-size: 1.45rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .02em;
}

.drop-cap {
  font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 2.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 0.8;
  margin-right: 3px;
  vertical-align: -4px;
}

.value-item p {
  max-width: 600px;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {

  .values-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

}

.values h2 {
  font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.featured-copy {
  max-width: 760px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.featured-photo {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.featured-photo img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
}

</style>